{"result": {"folders": ["lab2", "2017"], "nr": 1008, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "ie7xy8gtpwk1t5", "data": "j09hrus63h56xc", "type": "create", "when": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "j0ev4kprnoko", "type": "update", "when": "2017-03-18T06:18:45Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "j0nb6u7x86e4nf", "to": "j09hrus4f76xb", "type": "i_answer", "when": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "页机制中地址转换&#xff08;查找、修改&#xff09;", "created": "2017-03-18T06:18:45Z", "content": "<p>#查找页表</p>\n<p>cpu看到的都是线性地址&#xff0c;具体访存时放到总线上的地址是物理地址&#xff0c;在两者之间进行转换的是MMU&#xff0c;在MMU中通过查找页表项进行转换&#xff0c;过程如陈渝老师在视频中说的&#xff0c;也有对应的<a href=\"https://chyyuu.gitbooks.io/os_course_exercises/content/all/03-2-spoc-discussion.html\" target=\"_blank\">练习</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#修改页表项</p>\n<p>要如何修改页表项呢&#xff1f;就跟普通的往内存里写数据一样&#xff0c;但是我们只知道页目录表的物理地址&#xff08;CR3中&#xff09;&#xff0c;不知道它的线性地址。</p>\n<p>在ucore中&#xff0c;页目录表的&#xff08;逻辑&#xff09;线性地址是0xFAC00000&#xff0c;即是说&#xff0c;MMU会用这个地址查找PDE中的表项&#xff0c;而其中的内容正是PDE的首地址的物理页号。</p>\n<p>那么问题来了&#xff0c;假如我要修改PDE中第&#43;2项&#xff0c;要给它哪个地址呢&#xff1f;是0xFAFCB002吗&#xff1f;&#xff08;查PDE两次回到自己&#xff0c;offset 2&#xff09;</p>\n<p>要修改PDE中第&#43;2项指向的页表的第&#43;3项呢&#xff1f;</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "ie7xy8gtpwk1t5", "subject": "页机制中地址转换&#xff08;查找、修改&#xff09;", "created": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z", "content": "<p>#查找页表</p>\n<p>cpu看到的都是线性地址&#xff0c;具体访存时放到总线上的地址是物理地址&#xff0c;在两者之间进行转换的是MMU&#xff0c;在MMU中通过查找页表项进行转换&#xff0c;过程如陈渝老师在视频中说的&#xff0c;也有对应的<a href=\"https://chyyuu.gitbooks.io/os_course_exercises/content/all/03-2-spoc-discussion.html\" target=\"_blank\">练习</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#修改页表项</p>\n<p>要如何修改页表项呢&#xff1f;就跟普通的往内存里写数据一样&#xff0c;但是我们只知道页目录表的物理地址&#xff08;CR3中&#xff09;&#xff0c;不知道它的线性地址。</p>\n<p>在ucore中&#xff0c;页目录表的&#xff08;逻辑&#xff09;线性地址是0xFAC00000&#xff0c;即是说&#xff0c;MMU会用这个地址查找PDE中的表项&#xff0c;而其中的内容正是PDE的首地址的物理页号。</p>\n<p>那么问题来了&#xff0c;假如我要修改PDE中第&#43;2项&#xff0c;要给它哪个地址呢&#xff1f;是0xFAFCB002吗&#xff1f;&#xff08;查PDE两次回到自己&#xff0c;offset 2&#xff09;</p>\n<p>要修改PDE中第&#43;2项指向的页表的第&#43;3项呢&#xff1f;</p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["2017", "lab2", "student"], "tag_good": [{"role": "instructor", "name": "Yong XIANG", "endorser": {}, "admin": true, "photo": null, "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "photo_url": null, "us": false, "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "os2018spring_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "facebook_id": null}, {"role": "student", "name": "Chen TANG", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "jd612gjswfy2qt", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "unique_views": 185, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "j0nb6u7rv374ne", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "", "created": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z", "content": "<p>请尝试分析下面的几个函数和宏&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>mmu.h</p>\n<pre>#define PDX(la) ((((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PDXSHIFT) &amp; 0x3FF)<br />#define PTX(la) ((((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PTXSHIFT) &amp; 0x3FF)<br />#define PPN(la) (((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PTXSHIFT)<br />#define PGOFF(la) (((uintptr_t)(la)) &amp; 0xFFF)</pre>\n<p>glue_memlayout.h</p>\n<pre>#define VPT 0xFAC00000</pre>\n<p>pmm.c</p>\n<pre>void map_pgdir(pde_t * pgdir)</pre>\n<p>proc.c</p>\n<pre>static int setup_pgdir(struct mm_struct *mm)</pre>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie", "jd612gjswfy2qt"], "no_answer": 0, "id": "j09hrus4f76xb", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 6, "num_favorites": 2, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, 